summary: A collaboration with ChizFoShiz and his player voiceset mod
descriptionHtml:
Beware the dragonborn :D

THIS IS A MODDER'S RESOURCE.

It's an entirely new and brutal voice preset I created, and ChizFoShiz has offered to integrate it into his next release of the player voicesets mod here:

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51387/?

*Update 03/18/14*

ChizFoShiz just promised to add this to his next release ^^ So anyone out there who might want to contribute player voices, give it a shot! He's really great for doing all of the truly hard work with creation kit. He even knows how to sync player mouth movement with the comment system, which is truly epic.
author: wulfy4131
